    <!-- ── ACKNOWLEDGMENTS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="docs-section">
      <h2 class="docs-h2">Acknowledgments</h2>
      <p class="docs-body">
        CSL style based on <em>Bluebook Law Review</em> by Bruce D'Arcus, Nancy Sims, and contributors.
        Locator handling (at X, ¶ X, n.X) draws on Jonathan Choi's enhanced Bluebook style (2019).
        Further enhanced for Bluebook 22nd edition compliance and perma.cc archiving support.
      </p>
